<div id="banner">
  <h1>A website for sports administrators and students</h1></div>
<div id="bannercontent">This website is dedicated to students and teachers who need  information about the field of  Sport and Recreation Management. The site contains more than 500 freely available web pages and some resources which are downloadable for a small fee. The resources for Bookkeeping, Budgeting, Event Management and Sponsorship are widely used across the world. The site was initiated in 1998 to assist students locally in Brisbane Australia but increasingly resources are being developed to assist teachers with their classroom practise.</div>
